@wp.kernel
def expr_dbuvri(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.32)) * v1)
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.abs(tmp + 0.33) * (v0 + 0.35 - tmp + 0.19)))
    v0 = ((v1 - 0.77) * wp.abs(0.99))
    v1 = 0.78
    v0 = 0.28
    data[tid] = v0
